ERIC, PLEASE MAY I HAVE
YOUR MOTEL ROOM KEY, PLEASE?

22:12.456 --> 22:14.832
FEZ, I'M NOT GOING
TO A MOTEL WITH YOU.

22:15.000 --> 22:16.959
